channel.title: Half Life 2 - Capture the Flag 2.0 Released
channel.description:
[align=center][img]https://www.hl2ctf.com/themes/hl2ctfcom/images/hl2ctfhead01.jpg[/img]
Hello fellow gamers! Im one of the developers of HL2CTF.
The anticipation is over! Half - Life 2 : Capture The Flag 2.0 has been released! To be a part of this great FREE game, visit [url=https://www.hl2ctf.com]The HL2:CTF Website[/url] today!
